《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》於同日報導，美國航機實際上正在同時向日本和中國提交飛行報告，並儘量更改航線，避免進入該區域<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303562904579230894060384128 |title=Japan, U.S. at Odds Over China's Air Zone |accessdate=2013-12-02 |archive-date=2014-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320154532/http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303562904579230894060384128 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

